<div class="p">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Revel in the soldierly needles of the pine,</div>
<div class="p">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Each wat’ry bead aglitter on the morning lawn,</div>
<div class="p">The hatchling fern of late unfurled,</div>
<div class="p">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; The subtle quilted ripples in a spool of twine,</div>
<div class="p">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Each hair encompassed by the freckles of a fawn,</div>
<p> </p>
<div class="p">Diminutive worlds all around in min’ature,</div>
<div class="p">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Armies of enchanting stigmas in the flower,</div>
<div class="p">Of Autumn’s fallen greenery the ossature,</div>
<div class="p">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; And frantic creatures in a fallen tree’s bower.</div>
